#7300
HERO's TESTING GROUNDS~
You have just been transferred into a huge indoor combat room.  As you
peer around the room, you notice that it is very damp and dark.  As your
eyes adjust to the darkness, you notice that your light source begins to
flicker on and off.  On the floor, you notice blood and bones everywhere.
Broken weapons, armor, and potion bottles are scattered all over the floor.
There are no exits here therefore you can not flee.  To be a HERO you must
be among the bravest in Midgaard, thus fleeing can not be an option for
you. You must embrace Death with Dignity!
From the looks of things, you guess that many combats have occured here
and that many creatures have died here.  Now you know that it's your 
turn to DIE or to SURVIVE.  To Die means Failure.  To Survive means
you are worthy to be a HERO.
Good Luck!
~
