A {BO,Y}Trail{bo} to the {BO,R}Training Grounds{bo}~
   
   You are on a path to one of the oldest and greatest adventurer's 
   schools.  The best and most valiant warriors trained here.  The 
   great thieves learned their unique skills here.  The mysterious 
   mages of old created their deep dark magic here.  And the holy 
   clerics have practiced their arts of healing here.
  
   As a new player, you will need to learn the same skills and arts
   as these old and legendary heroes.  Even if you are an experienced 
   player we suggest you try our school.  You will probably find it
   to your benefit afterwards.
   
   Travel north to begin your training by typing: north or n
    
~
