#7352
Communications Room~
 
  There are several ways to communicate with others.  The simplest way
is to type : Say (your message).  You can also use (') in place of the
word Say.  Remember that the person you are talking to must be in the
same room you are in so that he/she will hear your words.
 
  In order to see which players are currently playing type : Who
You can also type (who lc) or (Who -lfc) to see other types of info.
There is a SIGN on the wall.
 
~
