0 -1 7351
E
sign~
 
       More complicated methods of communications can also be used.
 
Type: TELL (message) to talk to someone who is not in the same room as you.
 After they tell back to you, you can simply type REPLY to tell again.
Type CALL (name of person) then # (message) to communicate with someone you
 wish to have a longer conversation with. Type Call again to end the call.
Type SHOUT or SHO (message) if you have a message you want EVERYONE in the
 game to hear (please do not abuse this or the GODS will get angry).
Type GOSSIP or GOS (message) to be on the gossip channel.  The gossip channel
 is used for general conversations.
If you are in a group of adventurers you use GT (message) to talk to others
 within your group.
 
Other channels also available
    Flame  Trivia  Chat  (language channels) IRC Auction Whisper Ask 
~
