#7353
Social Skills~

  There are several different jestures you can do with your player, these
are know as social skills.  Type Help Social, to find out a list of stuff
you can do.  For example, if you want to make your player smile you type
Smile. IF you want to make your player bow you type Bow or Bow (person's
name). There are many different jestures or actions you can do here.
Please refer to the list. There is a SIGN on the wall.
 
