sign~
 
You may also gossip actions or emote by doing the following on any channel.
 
   Usage:  (channel) @<smile>
           (channel) @<smile> person
           (channel) , <emote> (the , is you and emotes are made up by you)
 
   Example:  Gossip You Smile Happily
             Gossip You Smile at him/her
             Gossip (You) stands on your head and looks silly
 
