#7354
Equipment Room~
 
  This mob holds several pieces of equipment which you will need to
start your journey through Northern Crossroads.  Some things you wear
(around various parts of your body) and some things you hold.  You wield or
hold weapons. A full inventory of equipment will consist of 18 items. They
are the following: 1 light source (which you hold) 15 items which you wear,
1 weapon which you Wield, and 1 weapon or item which you hold (ie. staffs,
etc.). Kill the mob and take its equipment and try wearing, wielding,
or holding them.  There will be others holding eq. be sure and kill them
all.
There is a Sign on the wall.
 
~
