E
sign~
 
  Good equipment is a vital part of the game.  Some equipment will improve
your armor class, some your mana, movement, or hit points. Most pieces of
equipment give some type of special ability.  To find out what a certain
piece of equipment does, you can use a scroll of identification on it.
Some equipment is aligned, you must be evil, netural, or good in order to
wear or use them.  Your alignment changes when you kill certain
types of monsters (or also called MOBS).  If you kill good mobs you will 
become more evil, and if you kill evil mobs you will become more good.
 
~
