#7355
Combat Room~
 
  There is a Mob in this room which you can try your fighting skills on.
You should be wielding a weapon first.  Type Hit or Kill (name of the mob)
to begin attacking it.  You will only stop attacking once you have killed
the monster or it has killed you.  You can also cast spells on it by typing
cast '(spell name)' (mob's name). Remember you can use spells only if you
have learned the spell before.  Good Luck!
There is a Sign on the wall

