sign~
 
  Before you begin fighting, you will need to see if the mob you will be
fighting is within your skill level.  In order to find out, you would type
Con (mob's name) or Con Mob (if you will fight the first mob in the room).
There will be a sentence telling you whether the mob is a good match for you.
Remember that before fight ANY unfamiliar mob, you should always "con it".
(By the way con = consider). 
