#7356
Maps~
 
  There are maps for both upper and lower Midgaard which you can look at.
You simply type Look Map or Look Lower or Upper.  These maps will be
important for you because it will familiarize you with the areas of town. 
In addition, you can type help area, for a list of areas you can visit and
what character levels you should be.  You can also type Help Area, for an
area map of all the areas of the Northern Crossroads. 
 
  Remember the first maps are objects you must carry with you in order to
use.  The second (area) map is built into the game, so you can type help
area anytime.
 
~
