#7357
Scores, Attributes, and Inventory~
 
  SCORE (or sc) will tell you various things about your character.
You can also type REPO to see your current hit points, mana points, and
movement. Type LEVEL and you will see how much expierence points you will
need to level your player.
 
Attribute (or att) will show you some other information about your character
such as your Armor class.
 
To see a list of what you are carrying type Inventory or inv.
 
