#7358
Leveling~
 
  You gain  exp. By killing mobs.  The highest level you can be as a mortal 
character is 50 Avatar.  At level 15, you will be able to get a Second class.
You may be a mage/cleric or any combination of the four.  You will be unable
to choose your second class.  When you reach level 15, go to Paladins Temple
and Pray at the altar. Ask any higher player where this is if you need help.
Remember to keep your CON and WIS as high as possible when you level your
player. This way you will gain the maximum amount of hit points and practices
when you level. You level your player in the room above Market Square.  Please 
refer to your maps for the location.
 
