#7361
Spells~
 
  Mage and Cleric's will have the abilities to cast spells. Casting spells
will cost you mana (the amount of mana depends on the spell you cast).  To
find out what spells you have type Practice or (pra).  To see a list of the
spells available type Spells.  To get a description on a certain spell,
type Help (spell name). You need to go to your guild to train to use your
spells. To use your spell abilities.  Type : Cast '(spell name)' (mob's name)
or cast '(spell name)' mob .  To cast the spell on the first mob (creature)
in the room.  Be careful when you use this because you can accidently cast a
spell on a mob that will Destroy you. Also, if a mob happens to wander into
the room and you press return, you will cast the spell on that mob.
 
  Example :  Cast 'chill touch' doggie  (always include ' in spell)
             Cast 'cure light' (self)
 
