  In case you are not able to flee, you may (if you are fast enough) try
to use a Scroll of Recall (which you can purchase at the magic shop) to
transport yourself to the Temple of Midgaard.  You do not have to hold the
Scroll of Recall in order to use it.  You just need to have it in your
inventory (but not within a container or a bag).  Some mobs will be able to
destroy your scroll in battle so be careful and make sure you still have
it when you recall.
 
