#7363
Wimpy~
 
  A good idea is to set your Wimpy.  Wimpy will automatically make you
flee in a battle when you reach a certain hit point.  For example, if you
have 20 hit points total and you want to flee from you opponent when you
reach 10 hit points you would type :  WIMPY 10.  Remember that when you flee from an opponent after you are engaged in a battle, you will loose some
expierence points. 
Now, go DOWN to the next room   then continue on by going WEST.
 
