#7365
Showexits and Auto Features~
 
  These two commands are very helpful when you play.  Type Showexits will
automatically show the exits from a room.  You can also type Exit (or Ex)
to show a room's exits.  Remember that this command will NOT show secret or
hidden exits.
 
  The Auto feature is also helpful here. Type Auto to see what Auto functions
are available to you.  For example, if you want to automatically take gold
from the corpses you would type : Auto Gold
 
