#7366
Secret Exits and Doors~
 
  There are many secret exits and hidden doors here on Nothern Crossroads.
Usually, there is something good behind these doors or passageways.  This
is how you find these types of doors.  When you are in a room type exit,
then try going in all the directions NOT listed when you type exit.  If
there is a hidden route then you will find it. In addition, your MUST read
the room descriptions VERY carefully to look for clues on possible Secret
Doors.
 
There is some sort of wooden door above you!!
 
