#7368
Invisibility~
 
  There are many things here which are invisibile. Equipment, objects, and
even some Players.  You will not be able to see these things if you don't
have some sort of detect invisibility spell, potion, or object. The simpliest
way to see invisible objects and people is to goto the Magic Shop in town and
buy a Yellow Potion.  This will allow you to see invisible things for a
certain amount of time. If you are invisible and you try to buy something at
the shops, the shop keepers will not do business with you.
 
