#7371
Eating and Drinking~
 
  From time to time you will get hungry or thirsty.  You need to eat food
and drink water.  You can buy food at the Bakery in town.  You can get
water at the fountain in Market Square.  You need to buy a barrel at the Bar
at the Hotel in town. After you buy a barrel, type POUR BARREL OUT.  This
will empty the barrel out and then go to the fountain and type FILL BARREL
FOUNTAIN.  When you are thirsty type Drink Barrel, and when you are hungry
type Eat (food name).
 
