#7372
Healing~
 
  When your are fighting Mobs, you will be loosing hit points when
the mob hits you.  If you are a cleric you can heal your self during
combat. You can also heal others when you are fighting.  If you are
a class other then a cleric, you will have to use potions to heal
yourself.  You can go to the the HEALER to buy potions to use in combat.
In order to use these potions just type: quaff (potion name).
 
