#7373
Resting & Sleeping~
 
  Another way you can regenerate your Hit points is to rest or sleep
after battles.  This will also regenerate your mana and movement
points. As you run out of mana, hit points, or movement type REST or
SLEEP and your points will regenerate. You will have faster regeneration
if you are resting in the Mallins. The mallins is located under Market
Square.  If the door to the mallins is closed just type OPEN Masuleaum.
 
