#7374
Repairing your equipment~
 
  You need to regularly repair your equipment. If you don't they will
dissappear after heavy use.  In order to check to see what your equipment's
condition is, take off the piece of eq, and type examine (name of eq).
To repair your eq, go to the smithy and type repair all. DO THIS OFTEN!!!
Remember it costs money to fix your stuff so have money ready before you
repair.
 
