#7375
Death Traps~
 
  In your many explorations you will probably run into a DEATH TRAP.
If you hit a DT. You will DIE and loose all your eq.  There will be NO
reimbursements for lost eq in a DT.  Therefore, try not to hit these
things. Most of the DT's will kill you instantly, but there are some
which will allow you to fly over them thus avoiding death.  You must
be wearing a piece of eq which will allow you to fly or have a fly
spell cast on you.  However, try to avoid ALL Dt's if you can.  One way
you can detect DT's is by using a thief's PEEK ability.  Simply peek to the
direction you wish to go. Peek more than once in case you fail! This is
one good reason to group.  Remember when you are in a new area, peek first
before entering into a room.
 
