SAVING~
 
  Ocasionally, the mud has crashes.  Remember to type SAVE often.
You should type save after every kill or if you get a piece of new
eq. Get use to typing save, in case of a crashe.  If the we have a
crashe and you did not type save you will not get your experience
points or eq. reimbursed.  The mud will automatically save your game
every 2 minutes or something BUT don't take that chance.
 
