#7379
ENERGY and MOVEMENT~
 
  Sometimes your evergy level and movement will run out.  This may happen
because you have walked too much or if you are wearing a piece of eq which
drains all your energy or if one of your spells runs out.  If this happens
you can do one of two things.  1) REST Sleep until your energy returns or
2) Eat something.  This should reset all your movement back to maximum.
 
