#7387
Donations & Sacrificing~
 
  There is a Donation room located in town where players can donate
equipment for others.  Please refer to the map for location. As a new
player it would be a good idea to check this room from time to time to
see if there is any useful equipment you can get. As you get more equipment
through your many adventures, you can donate some of you stuff to others.
To do this you type : Don (item).  This will automatically donate the
item directly to the donation room.  You do not have to Be in the Donation
room to donate.  Please Don't fill the donation room with Useless items.
If you want to get rid of an item PERMANENTLY you can sacrifice it to the
Gods.  Any item you sacrifice will be GONE!! So be careful when you do this.
You can sacrifice an item by typing :  Sac (item)
 
